   Of course, you should ask Gilbert in what sense she means quotidian.
   Form? Diction? Scenes? Portraits? I think Rae Armantrout and Fanny Howe
   manage it too. I'm sure there's more, but these are the first ones
   that come to mind (AND THIS IS NOT A VALUE JUDGMENT OVER WHICH L POETS
   ARE BETTER BY THE WAY)---best, cs
