Subject:      Re: poetics of the quotidian
 
>        Sandra Gilbert has "challenged" me to demonstrate the extent
to
>which "language poetry" (still perceived as a fairly homogenous group
among
>most academic poets) participates in a poetics of the quotidian.
>
