Rachel Blau DuPlessis' 'Draft 22' in the latest Hambone (#12)
takes impulse from the Philadelphia Wireman's sculptures, "found
abandoned on a side street in Philadelphia on a trash night in
1982." The cover bears a photo of one such sculpture, and photos
of three follow DuPlessis' draft...
 
 
