From:         Jonathan A Levin <jal17@COLUMBIA.EDU>
Subject:      Re: We all break for laokoon
In-Reply-To:  <v01520d04ad3d1db57ed7@[166.84.199.56]>
 
Jordan et al--
 
Glad you asked--a friend of mine, Joan Levinson, has a show running now
(through Feb 10, alas--Sat.) at the Nicholas Davies & Co. gallery, 23
Commerce St (b/t 7th Ave S and Bedford).  She makes sculpture with found
objects, w/ accompanying text.  Texts are gnomic and delightful-- a
poetic prose coming, in some ways, from Stein.  I hope you get a chance
to stop in--let me know if you do.
 
Jonathan Levin
