David -
 
Yes there is a tape of Larry Eigner reading at the Poetry Center at SFSU -
It is from November 29, 1984 and is the reading Larry did for co-winning
the Poetry Center Book Award in 1983 for Water/Places/A Time. He read with
Tina Darragh.
 
