>     and Ground Work III: Beyond Europe
> Rene Girard, The Martyrology
> Julie Dash, Daughters of the Dust
> 'AQL magazine (issues 1-4)
> Eileen Corder, Braids
> Halliday Dresser, Bird's Nest (For John Clare)
> Jeff Gburek Packet
> Pasolini, Collected Poems in Friulan Dialect
> Pat Reed, Kismet and We Want to See Your Tears Falling Down
>
>
> Weeks Five/Six: Dictation (James Merrill visit--by Ouija board)
>
> Merrill, The Changing Light at Sandovar
> Patience Worth Packet
> Rilke, Sonnets to Orpheus and Duino Elegies
> Yeats, A Vision
