laughing orgasms. Ron Silliman's "Sunset Debris" is better than any of the
Super-8 Triple-X I've seen. Gracious heavens, I even find Susan Howe's work
erotic in a way (fingertips carefully positioning the physical to achieve
maximal emotional weight) -- but my libido is probably not yours.
 
