Subject:      FYI - CDA has been signed into law
 
>Date: 15 Feb 1996 16:16:57 +0000 (GMT)
>From: jennifer_brannen@ucc.ie
>Subject: FYI - this scared me to pieces re:1st amendment, pass along
>Sender: Jennifer Brannen <ARIH6021@bureau.ucc.ie>
>To: jbrannen@infolink.morris.mn.us
>X-Envelope-To: jbrannen@infolink.morris.mn.us
>X-Vms-To: IN%"jbrannen@infolink.morris.mn.us"
