CDA and Electronic Books]
>
>Date: 14 Feb 1996 11:42:00 -0600 (CST)
>From: Jon Noring <noring@netcom.com>
>Subject: --> Press Release from OmniMedia Regarding the CDA and Electronic
Books
>Sender: "TEI (Text Encoding Initiative) public discussion list"
> <TEI-L@UICVM.CC.UIC.EDU>
>To: Multiple recipients of list TEI-L <TEI-L@UICVM.CC.UIC.EDU>
>Reply-to: Jon Noring <noring@netcom.com>
>X-Envelope-to: cournane@curia.ucc.ie, pflynn@curia.ucc.ie
>Content-transfer-encoding: 7BIT
>Approved-By:  tei-l <U59467@UICVM.BITNET>
