"Poetic Artifice" is also worth noting again: this is V F-T's "Theory of
Twentieth-Century Poetry", published by Manchester Univ. Press, 1978. Her
"Collected Poems and Translations" (Allardyce Barnett 1990) also includes,
as has been noted, "Poetry Such As: An Introduction to the Poetry of Tel
Quel" with translations of Pleynet & Roche. All good things.
 
