Gonna leave you now,
Goin' anyhow,
Know where I'm bound,
I'm just packin up gettin ready to go.
 
I'm packin one shoebox for all my clothes
(just packin' up gettin ready to go)
Got so little to carry and so far to go
(just packin up gettin ready to go)
 
Well you can read my lips, you can't read my mind
(just packin up)
I'm leavin now, gotta leave you behind
(packin up)
 
Now there's only one thing worryin my mind
(just packin up)
Somebody's gonna enjoy what I'm leavin behind
(Just packin up...gettin ready... to go)
 
bye bye Brownie
