Mark,
I was teaching sound and poetry
to some sixth graders
and at one point they all
began singing A B C D E F G
H I J K L M
and I stopped them there (I didn't
have much time). I realized later that they
were just getting to the good part.
Alpha beta gamma delta epsilon eta
theta iota kappa lambda mu nu ksi...
in the bereshith in the zohar
aren't aleph and beth
given precedence for their modesty?
Jordan
