Industrial Workers of the World to organize the booksellers.  If you've ever
worked in retail you don't need to ask why.  Borders management in Ann Arbor is
dispatching lawyers to 17th and Walnut quicker than you can special order the
Martha Stewart Anarchist hors d'oeuvre book. That's all I know right now.
Anybody else?
 
 
